{
  "stem": "5275.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He should not pay the school director, but keep the money to himself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I have another name now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm informing you and Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wladyslaw B.'-- I don't know who he is-- 'he, if he wants to, may send a parcel from time to time to Romana Halperin.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] Warm gloves for Stephen can be picked up on the [NON-ENGLISH] Square, third floor, Maria Sufa.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A sweater and handkerchiefs [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] are [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They will try to get a confession from Stephen by beating him that I'm his mother, but he cannot admit to something that is not true.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Krisia, I know that you have it not easy yourself, but have pity on him, bless him on his new part of life.' [CRYING] That was the last I heard.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[DRINKS] [SIGHS] I was an A student, and this was three weeks before the final exams.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I failed them all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And the director told the teachers that I have lost my mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they gave me completion, that they knew because they felt that I was an A student all  the time, and they understood why I couldn't do the final exams.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The director and his wife were marvelous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They obviously realized what has happened and they told me I can stay there as long as I want to.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was working on the farm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know why the Germans didn't come after me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't understand what Mother meant, they know my address.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They  didn't come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe because it was too late in the war, they already were trying to escape, which the Russian front was already coming.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
